    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    App
    The main entry point of the housing project management application.
    Applicant
    Represents an applicant in the housing system.
    ApplicantApplicationService
    Service class for handling applicant-related application logic.
    ApplicantApplicationView
     
    ApplicantController
    Controller class that is responsible for handling applicant-related actions.
    ApplicantRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing applicants in the system.
    Application
    Represents an application made by an applicant for a project.
    ApplicationRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing application data.
    ApplicationService
    Service class for managing housing application operations.
    ApplicationStatus
    Represents the different statuses of an application.
    AuthController
    Controller class to handle authentication processes.
    AuthenticationException
    Exception thrown when authentication fails.
    AuthService
    Service class for handling user authentication and password management.
    AuthView
    View class for authentication-related interactions and role-based menus.
    CommonView
    View class for displaying messages and prompting user input in the console.
    CsvReader
    Utility class for reading CSV files into a list of key-value maps.
    CsvWriter
    Utility class for writing data to CSV files.
    DateTimeUtils
    Utility class for parsing and formatting LocalDateTime objects.
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry made by an applicant regarding a project.
    EnquiryController
    Controller class for managing applicant and project enquiries.
    EnquiryRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing enquiry data.
    EnquiryService
    Service class for managing property enquiry operations.
    EnquiryStatus
    Represents the different statuses of an enquiry.
    EnquiryView
    View class for displaying and managing enquiry-related views.
    FilterView
    View class responsible for handling the display and interaction related to filtering projects.
    FlatType
    Represents the types of flats available.
    Hash
    Utility class for hashing strings and verifying hashed values using SHA-256.
    IApplicantApplicationService
    Interface for applicant-related application logic.
    IApplicationService
    Interface for managing housing application operations.
    IAuthService
    Interface for handling user authentication and password management.
    IBaseRepository<T>
    Interface for basic operations on a repository.
    ICommonView
    Interface for common view operations.
    ICsvConfig
    Interface for handling CSV file configuration.
    IEnquiryService
    Interface for managing property enquiry operations.
    IManagerService
    Interface for manager-specific service operations.
    IOfficerRegistrationService
    Interface for managing officer registrations for projects.
    IOfficerRegistrationView
    Interface for displaying information related to officer registration.
    IOfficerService
    Interface for managing officer-related operations.
    IProjectService
    Interface for managing project-related operations.
    IProjectView
    Interface for displaying project-related information to the user.
    IRegistrationService
    Interface for services related to the registration process for projects.
    Manager
    Represents a manager in the system who oversees a project.
    ManagerController
    Controller for handling all actions available to a Manager user.
    ManagerRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing manager data.
    ManagerService
    Service class for managing operations related to managers, such as generating reports and exporting data to CSV files.
    ManagerView
    View class that handles the display of manager-related functionalities.
    MaritalStatus
    Represents the marital status of an individual.
    Officer
    Represents an officer in the system who is a type of applicant with additional roles.
    OfficerApplication
    Represents an officer's application for a project.
    OfficerController
    Handles all operations related to Officer actions in the housing project management system.
    OfficerRegistration
    Represents an officer's registration for a project.
    OfficerRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing officer data.
    OfficerService
    Service class for managing officer-related operations.
    OfficerView
    View class that handles the display of officer-related functionalities.
    Project
    Represents a housing project managed by a manager with various flat types and applicants.
    ProjectController
    Handles all operations related to project management in the housing project system.
    ProjectRepository
    Repository class responsible for managing project data.
    ProjectService
    Service class for managing project-related operations.
    ProjectView
    View class responsible for displaying project-related functionalities.
    Receipt
    Represents a receipt issued for a housing project booking by an applicant.
    ReceiptRepository
    Repository for managing receipts, including loading from and saving to CSV files.
    ReceiptView
    View class responsible for displaying receipt-related details and success messages.
    Registration
    Represents a registration for a housing project.
    RegistrationRepository
    Repository for managing registrations, including loading from and saving to CSV files.
    RegistrationService
    Provides services related to the registration process for projects.
    RegistrationStatus
    Represents the status of a registration.
    Role
    Represents the different roles in the system.
    User
    Represents a user in the system, which can be an applicant/officer/manager.
    UserRepository
    Repository for managing users, including loading from and saving to a CSV file.
    ValidationUtils
    Utility class for input validation.
